                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-1440" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY BERRY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a baker, and live at Woolwich. On the 16th of February I was in the street at Woolwich—I saw the prisoner takes coat from inside the door of Mr. Birt's shop—he walked away with it—I ran into the shop—I afterwards saw him again in High-street, and pointed him out to the policeman, who took him—he is the person.</p>
